data.text:
Sandy Lam and Tsung-Sheng Lee are divorced after a marriage of 6 years. They had 1 child.

They had a daughter named Renee age 26.

About

Sandy Lam is a 58 year old Hong Konger Musician born on 26th April, 1966 in Hong Kong. Her zodiac sign is Taurus

Tsung-Sheng Lee is a 66 year old Taiwanese Music Producer born on 19th July, 1958 in Beitou, Taipei, Taiwan. His zodiac sign is Cancer
